ounds unchanged after translations. Furthermore, we\ndemonstrate the contribution of each component in SoloGAN by ablation studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Aug 2020 16:31:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Feb 2022 05:58:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 28 Jun 2022 18:35:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-30"}
