 survey, will detect $\\gtrsim$ 15 000 galaxies (3\n$\\sigma$ significance) at 50-200 Mpc, which is ~100X more normal galaxies than\ndetected in any X-ray survey to date.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Aug 2020 22:41:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-19"}
