ICE run\n2 preliminary results for neutral meson production in pp and Pb--Pb collisions\nat LHC energies are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Aug 2020 10:25:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
