 division between energy and entropy\nelasticity is investigated in detail with regard to the experimental setup.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Aug 2020 11:38:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Dec 2020 18:45:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-09"}
